quoteFirst: Seven minutes proved to be nearer the mark. In response to a hail from within the wall, several of the warders bent to the windlass, whereupon the portcullis scraped and groaned aloft, and the tall knight came riding out just as the hands of Mallory's timepiece registered
title: A Knyght Ther Was
author: Young, Robert F., 1915-1986; Summers, Leo, 1925-1985 [Illustrator]
